---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="Where life begins - Learn about River of Life, a loving community of Christ-followers in Henry, IL.">
  <PageHero title="About Us" image="/hero/7.jpg" />

  <section class="content">
    <div class="section">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>ROL is a loving community of Christ-followers dedicated to serving people on their spiritual journey. We exist to help people find and follow Jesus. Whether you're exploring faith for the first time or have been walking with God for years, there's a place for you here.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>What to Expect</h2>
      <p>When you visit River of Life, you'll find a friendly, welcoming atmosphere. Our services include contemporary worship music and practical, Bible-based teaching. We have programs for kids and students so the whole family can grow together.</p>
      <p>Come as you are - there's no dress code. We'd love to meet you!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Service Times</h2>
      <div class="service-times-list">
        <div class="service-day">
          <h3>Sunday</h3>
          <p>Christian Education - 10:00am</p>
          <p>Main Service - 11:00am</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-day">
          <h3>Wednesday</h3>
          <p>Midweek Bible Study - 7:00pm</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Location</h2>
      <p>425 University Ave<br />Henry, IL 61537</p>
      <p><a href="tel:+13093643165">(309) 364-3165</a></p>
      <a href="/directions" class="btn">Get Directions</a>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-section">
      <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
      <p>Get to know the leaders who serve at River of Life.</p>
      <a href="/team" class="btn">View Our Team</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .section h2 {
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .section p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .service-times-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-day {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold);
  }

  .service-day h3 {
    color: var(--color-teal);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .service-day p {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
</style>
